itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway throw an impromptu rager at a strip club in Houston, Texas the night before the Drinkin' Bros cruise with 40 drunk soon to be passengers... and things got out of control.  This is the craziest show since Episode #100.  We also pull some of the strippers off stage to share their life stories. This was complete madness.
